{"iti10:0.1":"Itivuttaka 10 ","iti10:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","iti10:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti10:0.4":"Dosaparinnasutta ","iti10:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti10:2.1":"“Dosam, bhikkhave, anabhijanam aparijanam tattha cittam avirajayam appajaham abhabbo dukkhakkhayaya. ","iti10:2.2":"Dosanca kho, bhikkhave, abhijanam parijanam tattha cittam virajayam pajaham bhabbo dukkhakkhayaya”ti. ","iti10:2.3":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti10:2.4":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti10:3.1":"“Yena dosena dutthase, ","iti10:3.2":"satta gacchanti duggatim; ","iti10:3.3":"Tam dosam sammadannaya, ","iti10:3.4":"pajahanti vipassino; ","iti10:3.5":"Pahaya na punayanti, ","iti10:3.6":"imam lokam kudacanan”ti. ","iti10:4.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti10:4.2":"Dasamam. ","iti10:4.3":"Patibhogavaggo pathamo. ","iti10:5.0":"Tassuddanam ","iti10:5.1":"Ragadosa atha moho, ","iti10:5.2":"Kodhamakkha manam sabbam; ","iti10:5.3":"Manato ragadosa puna dve, ","iti10:5.4":"Pakasita vaggamahu pathamanti. "}